{
  "stem": "10588.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Yiddish literature-- in fact, I have a story, which is really amazing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, we didn't have, like we have now, built-in closets, you know, like, sliding doors.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "What we had was called a French armoire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, it's like a-- it was a chest, a tall chest, that reached almost from the floor to the ceiling.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it had two doors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "When you faced it, this, the right-hand side was a little bit narrower, broader than the other one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "One was usually used for the wardrobe.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the other side, it was linen, nicely-pressed linen, and with ribbons around, and the very highest had shelf in it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "For some reason, when I was a little girl, the door where the wardrobe was supposed to be was always locked.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I couldn't figure out why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I used to play all kinds of games.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, I was a very imaginative child.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, since earliest childhood, I had a wonderful imagination.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was a curious child, and my family always encouraged that curiosity.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I used to think, guessing games-- maybe a skeleton, maybe a treasure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I even went as far as to think maybe I was adopted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't understand, why is it locked?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one time, my mother said, 'Itkele, please come.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I want to show you something.' I was trembling with fear and excited with anticipation simultaneously, wondering what is in that closet here and what's so important?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother took the key, opened the closet, and there was a whole chest-- it was a closet, was that [INAUDIBLE] of the chest, full with books-- poetry books and, and other books, you know, beautiful bound books.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
